<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 2001. aasta 1. aprillil. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act enters into force on 1 April 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Laevapere liikme ja reederi v&otilde;i muu t&ouml;&ouml;andja vahel s&otilde;lmitud meret&ouml;&ouml;leping peab olema viidud koosk&otilde;lla k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 8 s&auml;testatuga 2001. aasta 1. oktoobriks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Seafarers' contracts of employment entered into by crew members and shipowners or any other employers shall be brought into accordance with the provisions of &sect; 8 of this Act by 1 October 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Enne 2001. aasta 1. aprilli toimepandud distsiplinaars&uuml;&uuml;tegude menetlemine toimub vastavalt t&ouml;&ouml;tajate distsiplinaarvastutuse seaduses (RT I 1993, 26, 441; 1995, 16, 228; 1998, 64/65, 1009; 2000, 102, 674) s&auml;testatud korrale. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Proceedings concerning disciplinary offences committed prior to 1 April 2001 shall be conducted pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Employees Disciplinary Punishments Act (RT I 1993, 26, 441; 1995, 16, 228; 1998, 64/65, 1009; 2000, 102, 674). (1) RT = Riigi Teataja = State Gazette </inglise>
